208";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Heavy_Mass";s:4:"text";s:20:"Shard would read it~";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1386724647";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13867246470";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#1f89e2";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:132213;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"132213";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Heavy_Mass";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:4:"text";s:89:"The letter bore the seal and letterhead of the Fillydelphia Academy for Higher Sciences. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1386724905";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13867249087";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:132214;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"132214";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Heavy_Mass";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:4:"text";s:25:"Dear Miss Crystal Shard, ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1386724917";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13867249205";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:132221;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"132221";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Heavy_Mass";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:4:"text";s:691:"It is with great pleasure that we write to you today to extend you the opportunity to join us at this most prestigious academy! We have for quite some time now been in need of a part time Alchemy professor, and you have come very highly recommended to us. We would like to have the chance to speak with you and get you settled before the beginning of the next semester, should you accept the position. Please write back immediately at the enclosed address and let us know when you will be available. Travel arrangements will be prepared and enclosed with our return correspondence. Thank you for your reply and welcome to our family! - Regards, Dean Bitterman. Chairman of the Hiring Board. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1386725322";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13867253255";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:132222;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"132222";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"25";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Heavy_Mass";s:12:"character_id";N;s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:4:"text";s:186:"There was also a hoofwritten note inside which fell out. -This position includes a lab. I expect you to finish your glass experiment before the end of the semester. Regards, Heavy Mass. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1386725370";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:5:"white";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13867253735";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:5:"white";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";s:1:"0";}i:132226;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"132226";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Heavy_Mass";s:4:"text";s:471:"Shard would, with some obvious glee, accept! Traditionally full professors were salary and tenured possitions! And if the teaching component was only part time, that meant it was primarily a university research post! WHich meant she could possibly have a staff.. maybe not direct assistant professors, as theyre usually tenured as well, but adjunct professors and lecturers might be available to her.. oh, but now she&#039;ll ahve to begin applying for research grants...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1386725974";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"13867259741";s:15:"chat_text_colo